            "rewritten_speech": "Hey everyone, just a heads up! Even though this Southport thing isn't in court yet, we need to be super careful with what we say. It’s a big deal and we don’t want to mess up any future trial. Let’s stick to talking about the emergency services or support for families without diving into who’s guilty or not. 🤔"
