            "rewritten_speech": "The IFN has been running since 1987, bringing different faiths together. It’s been backed by the government for ages. They were told they'd lose funding last year even before the new board member came in! They were promised money for this year too, but nope, that didn’t happen. Isn’t cutting off our main way of fostering Muslim-Jewish dialogue a big miss during these times? Why didn’t the Secretary meet with us to talk things over before deciding?"
