            "speakername": "Felicity Buchan",
            "rewritten_speech": "I agree, inter-faith work is useful! In my diverse area, I've connected mosques, synagogues, churches, and gurdwaras. But, we make it clear: find other funding, IFN. We can’t support them with MCB in the mix."
