{
    "speeches": [
        {
            "speakername": "Marion Fellows",
            "rewritten_speech": "Hey, Minister! We need to sort out this mess with the Post Office board. What are you doing to restore public trust after all those avalanches at the Business and Trade Committee yesterday? 📉"
